description: This file defines a mock catalog for an audiobook store frontend. It provides a static method that returns a list of sample Audiobook objects with predefined data such as id, title, author, price, and asset paths.

classes.name: MockCatalog
classes.description: A utility class that provides a static method to generate a mock list of audiobooks for UI or testing purposes.

methods.name: items
methods.description: Returns a list of predefined Audiobook instances representing sample titles in the catalog.
